Package: spacom
Type: Package
Title: Spatially weighted context data for multilevel modelling
Version: 0.9-4
Date: 2011-11-27
Author: Till Junge <till.junge@unil.ch>, Sandra Penic
        <sandra.penic@unil.ch>, Guy Elcheroth <guy.elcheroth@unil.ch>
Maintainer: Till Junge <till.junge@unil.ch>
Description: Constructs and describes spatially weighted context data
        from micro-level survey data by aggregation or from precise
        contextual indicators. Performs multilevel analyses where
        spatially weighted context data are combined with individual
        level predictor and outcome variables. Computes robust point
        estimates and standard errors by stratified resampling.
        Provides estimates of explained spatial dependency.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: methods, R (>= 2.10-0), spdep, foreach, lme4, boot
Packaged: 2012-05-30 20:42:52 UTC; junge
Repository: CRAN
Date/Publication: 2012-05-31 13:00:53
